# Creating Birthday Card Application:

Procedure:
Open new project using Android Studio
Select Empty Activity Template
Select API19: Android 4.4(kitkat) as minimum SDK
Give Finish and run the your app.


# Adding Text View in the layout:

Procedure:
Select Text View from the layout editor
Add Wishes in the Text View
Drag & drop the Text View from the palette
Change the margin (If required)
Confirm the text and give enter

#Procedure to change the format & color of the text:

~you can change the size and color of your text by using common attributes section
~Run to see the output.
